# Config YAML Rules

- Top-level key must be `roverrobotics_driver: ros__parameters:`.
- Required fields per robot: `robot_type`, `comm_type`, `device_port`, kinematics (`wheel_radius`, `wheel_base`, etc.), topic names, `odom_frame_id`, `odom_child_frame_id`.
- `robot_type` must match a supported protocol in the driver (see `.cursor/MEMORY.md`).
- Sensor toggles belong in `accessories.yaml`, not duplicated in every robot config.
- Copy nearest robot config and adjust values; do not strip commented optional params without reason.
